I knew that I was going to have to do

00:00:10.080 --> 00:00:12.004
a medical exam for immigration

00:00:12.005 --> 00:00:14.291
but I didn't know when in the process

00:00:14.292 --> 00:00:15.723
that was supposed to happen

00:00:16.160 --> 00:00:19.219
um when you apply for permanent residency

00:00:19.220 --> 00:00:20.649
in the application

00:00:20.650 --> 00:00:22.679
they tell you to wait until

00:00:22.680 --> 00:00:23.779
they tell you to go

00:00:23.780 --> 00:00:25.559
so they sent me um

00:00:25.560 --> 00:00:26.919
it looks like it was sent to me

00:00:26.920 --> 00:00:28.599
like on May 20th

00:00:28.600 --> 00:00:29.059
this year

00:00:29.060 --> 00:00:31.738
so it was like a month after

00:00:32.081 --> 00:00:33.418
I ended up

00:00:33.720 --> 00:00:35.895
applying for my permanent residency

00:00:35.896 --> 00:00:39.065
but they send you a notification with a letter

00:00:39.066 --> 00:00:41.559
with instructions that essentially show you

00:00:41.560 --> 00:00:44.073
and tell you what you are supposed to do

00:00:44.186 --> 00:00:46.855
um what you're supposed to bring

