I had called the physician

00:00:52.994 --> 00:00:55.569
that was approved to do it beforehand

00:00:55.570 --> 00:00:57.083
just to kind of get more information

00:00:57.084 --> 00:00:58.719
about the cost

00:00:58.720 --> 00:01:00.764
when you go through the immigration

00:01:00.765 --> 00:01:01.729
medical physical

00:01:01.730 --> 00:01:03.159
they tell you

00:01:03.160 --> 00:01:05.099
that this is an out of pocket cost

00:01:05.100 --> 00:01:06.739
and that you would have to confirm that

00:01:06.740 --> 00:01:08.380
with the labs and

00:01:09.320 --> 00:01:10.208
positions office

00:01:10.209 --> 00:01:11.648
that you're going to

00:01:11.649 --> 00:01:13.702
so I will also be sharing that

00:01:13.703 --> 00:01:14.979
cause I have receipts for all of that

00:01:14.980 --> 00:01:16.689
I won't show you the actual receipt

00:01:16.690 --> 00:01:17.975
but I have the numbers

00:01:18.169 --> 00:01:20.859
um but basically when I

00:01:20.860 --> 00:01:22.507
when I went to go do the physical

00:01:22.508 --> 00:01:23.419
I had a lot

00:01:23.420 --> 00:01:24.931
of medical anxiety

00:01:25.148 --> 00:01:27.996
um I have always had medical anxiety

00:01:27.997 --> 00:01:28.776
so when I was there

00:01:28.777 --> 00:01:30.736
I had some pretty high blood pressure

00:01:30.737 --> 00:01:32.547
that they were a little bit worried about

00:01:32.548 --> 00:01:33.697
but throughout the appointment

00:01:33.698 --> 00:01:35.676
it was going down pretty consistently

00:01:35.677 --> 00:01:37.679
so he he felt much better about it

00:01:37.680 --> 00:01:39.071
by the end of the

00:01:39.280 --> 00:01:40.740
physical um

