during the physical

00:01:42.321 --> 00:01:43.918
they essentially

00:01:44.441 --> 00:01:45.179
just ask you

00:01:45.180 --> 00:01:45.889
a bunch of questions

00:01:45.890 --> 00:01:47.240
about your health

00:01:47.241 --> 00:01:48.659
your previous history

00:01:48.660 --> 00:01:49.479
as far as like

00:01:49.480 --> 00:01:49.829
your health

00:01:49.830 --> 00:01:50.920
your mental health

00:01:50.921 --> 00:01:52.238
drug use alcohol

00:01:52.239 --> 00:01:53.139
things like that

00:01:53.140 --> 00:01:54.009
normal questions

00:01:54.010 --> 00:01:54.959
that you would go through

00:01:54.960 --> 00:01:56.379
on what I would think

00:01:56.380 --> 00:01:57.878
is any physical

00:01:58.040 --> 00:01:59.226
um from there

00:01:59.227 --> 00:02:00.752
they listen to your breathing

00:02:00.753 --> 00:02:03.509
um I did have to undress

00:02:03.510 --> 00:02:06.271
in order for them to um

00:02:06.680 --> 00:02:08.659
to essentially examine my skin

00:02:08.660 --> 00:02:11.499
but they don't touch any private part

00:02:11.500 --> 00:02:12.380
of your body

00:02:12.381 --> 00:02:13.854
um and the doctor

00:02:13.855 --> 00:02:14.619
that I had

00:02:14.620 --> 00:02:16.958
was very open about um

00:02:17.701 --> 00:02:19.379
me being comfortable with him

00:02:19.380 --> 00:02:20.539
and so he had

00:02:20.540 --> 00:02:24.599
even offered to bring in a female assistant to

00:02:24.600 --> 00:02:26.589
um to view

00:02:26.590 --> 00:02:28.574
while I was being examined

00:02:28.611 --> 00:02:29.499
um and so

00:02:29.500 --> 00:02:30.750
I really appreciated him

00:02:30.751 --> 00:02:31.939
being mindful of that

00:02:31.940 --> 00:02:32.854
of course

00:02:33.200 --> 00:02:34.709
um overall

00:02:34.710 --> 00:02:36.929
the physical portion of the medical exam

00:02:36.930 --> 00:02:38.535
lasted about an hour

00:02:38.536 --> 00:02:39.339
um with all of

00:02:39.340 --> 00:02:39.913
like the waiting

